\c 45
\s Rwiyo pamutambo waMambo Mukuru
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weShoshanimi; Pisarema ravanakomana vaKora. Rwiyo rweMashiri. Rwiyo rworudo.
\p
\v 1 Mwoyo wangu unotutuma namashoko akanaka; Ndinotaura zvinhu zvandakaita zvinoreva mambo; Rurimi rwangu ipeni yomunyori anokurumidza kunyora.
\v 2 Imi makanaka-naka kupfuura vana vavanhu; Nyasha yakadururirwa pamiromo yenyu; Saka Mwari wakakuropafadzai nokusingaperi.
\v 3 Sungai munondo wenyu pachiuno chenyu, imi wamasimba, Ukuru hwenyu nohumambo hwenyu.
\v 4 Fambai noumambo hwenyu muchikunda, Nokuda kwezvokwadi nounyoro nokururama; Ruoko rwenyu rworudyi ngarukudzidzisei zvinotyisa.
\v 5 Miseve yenyu inopinza; Vanhu vanokundwa nemi; Inobaya pamwoyo yavavengi vamambo.
\v 6 Chigaro chenyu choushe, imi Mwari, chiripo nokusingaperi-peri; Tsvimbo youshe hwenyu itsvimbo yakarurama.
\v 7 Makada kururama, mukavenga kusarurama; Naizvozvo Mwari, Mwari wenyu wakakuzodzai Namafuta okufara kupfuura shamwari dzenyu.
\v 8 Nguo dzenyu dzose dzinonhuwira nemura nearosi neakasia; Madimbwa akakufadzai achiridzwa mudzimba dzamambo dzenyanga dienz.ou.
\v 9 Vakunda vamadzimambo vari pakati pavanhukadzi venyu vanokudzwa; Paruoko rwenyu rworudyi vahosi vamire vakashonga ndarama ye Ofiri.
\v 10 Terera mukunda, rangarira, urereke nzeve yako; Kanganwawo vanhu vako, neimba yababa vako;
\v 11 Ipapo mambo achada kunaka kwako; Nokuti ndiye Ishe wako; unamate kwaari iwe.
\v 12 Uye mukunda weTiro achavapo nechipo; Vapfumi pakati pavanhu vachakumbira ngoni dzako.
\v 13 Mukunda wamambo akanaka kwazvo-kwazvo mukati meimba yamambo; Nguo dzake dzakarukwa nendarama.
\v 14 Uchaperekwa kuna mambo nenguo dzakarukwa dzinamavara; Mhandara, shamwari dzake dzinomutevera, Vachaiswa kwamuri.
\v 15 Vachaperekwa nomufaro nokufarisisa; Vachapinda mumba mamambo.
\v 16 Panzvimbo yamadzibaba ako vana vako vachavapo, Vauchaita machinda panyika yose.
\v 17 Ndichayeudzira zita renyu kusvikira kumarudzi ose; Naizvozvo ndudzi dzavanhu dzichakuvongai nokusingaperi-peri.
